    <detaileddescription>
<para>Pass in a market model, a list of instruments, and possible bumps.</para>
<para>Get out pseudo-root bumps that shift each implied vol by one percent, and leave the other instruments fixed.</para>
<para>If the contribution of an instrument is too correlated with other instruments used, discard it. </para>
